### Ping
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ping

### List books
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?page=1&size=10

### Search books
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/search?q=Library&page=1&size=5

### Search members
GET http://localhost:8000/api/members/search?q=Member&page=1&size=5

### Create a book
POST http://localhost:8000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "ISBN900101",
  "title": "Django Library API",
  "author": "Research Student",
  "published_year": 2026,
  "available_copies": 7
}

### Create a member
POST http://localhost:8000/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "membership_no": "M900101",
  "full_name": "Django Test Member",
  "email": "django.member@example.com"
}

### Checkout a book
POST http://localhost:8000/api/loans/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "book_id": 1,
  "member_id": 1,
  "loan_date": "2026-04-14",
  "due_date": "2026-04-28"
}

### Active loans
GET http://localhost:8000/api/loans/active?memberId=1&page=1&size=10

### Renew a loan
POST http://localhost:8000/api/loans/1/renew
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "due_date": "2026-05-05"
}

### Return a loan
POST http://localhost:8000/api/loans/1/return

### Expanded loans
GET http://localhost:8000/api/loans/expanded?page=1&size=10

### Stats
GET http://localhost:8000/api/stats
